#: ../../../release_details/9.4/delimited-text-reader-performances.md:1
msgid "Delimited Text Reader Performances"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/delimited-text-reader-performances.md:3
msgid ""
"vtkDelimitedTextReader memory footprint is now much lower during "
"computation. (i.e. inside the `RequestData`, called from `Update`) Also, "
"speedup are expected (due to the drastic diminution of allocations)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/delimited-text-reader-performances.md:7
msgid ""
"While it used to store the whole data as string before doing the conversion "
"to numeric values (if relevant) leading to data duplication at some point of "
"the process, it now performs conversion on the fly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/delimited-text-reader-performances.md:11
msgid ""
"There is no change once `RequestData` return, also no change in the output "
"`vtkTable`. This is a memory reduction *during the read process*."
msgstr ""

